#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-07-10-quarkus-langchain4j-opa-guardrails.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Implementing OPA-based guardrails in Quarkus LangChain4j provides:"
msgstr "在 Quarkus LangChain4j 中实现基于 OPA 的防护措施，可提供："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-07-10-quarkus-langchain4j-opa-guardrails.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Performance*: Sub-millisecond for pattern-matched prompts, vs seconds for LLM-based checks"
msgstr "*性能* ：模式匹配提示的响应时间在毫秒以内，而基于大型语言模型（LLM）的检查则需要数秒"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-07-10-quarkus-langchain4j-opa-guardrails.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Cost*: LLM-related costs decrease as the Wasm based validation success rate increases"
msgstr "*成本* ：随着基于 Wasm 的验证成功率提高，LLM 相关的成本随之降低"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-07-10-quarkus-langchain4j-opa-guardrails.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "*Flexibility*: Easy policy updates without code changes"
msgstr "*灵活性* ：无需修改代码即可轻松更新策略"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-07-10-quarkus-langchain4j-opa-guardrails.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"*Separate policy life cycle management*: The lifecycle of OPA-based guardrails can be managed independently of the\n"
"application lifecycle."
msgstr "*独立的策略生命周期管理* ：基于 OPA 的防护措施的生命周期可以独立于应用程序的生命周期进行管理。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-07-10-quarkus-langchain4j-opa-guardrails.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"*Platform independent implementation*: A Wasm OPA guardrail works the same across different platforms\n"
"(JVM/Node/Python, etc.)"
msgstr "*平台无关的实现* ：Wasm OPA 防护机制在不同平台（JVM/Node/Python 等）上的工作原理完全一致。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _posts/2026-07-10-quarkus-langchain4j-opa-guardrails.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The combination of Quarkus LangChain4j's guardrail framework, OPA policies and Wasm integration creates a robust\n"
"security layer implementation for AI applications."
msgstr "Quarkus LangChain4j 的 Guardrail 框架、OPA 策略以及 Wasm 集成相结合，为人工智能应用程序构建了一个强大的安全层实现。"

